reviewText: THIS BOY HIT THE SCENES AND RIPPED THE RAP WORLD OFF THE HINGES.  NOT ABOUT AN IMAGE. ALL REAL LIFE PAIN AND EXPERIENCES.  HE'S MAKING AMENDS WITH HIS PAST AND MOVING TOWARDS CHRIST.  ALWAYS WAS NEVER FAR FROM GOD.  NO RAPPER EVER SAYS A PRAYER ON EVERY CD.  I HAVE ALWAYS BEEN A CHRISTIAN SO I CAN RELATE ON GROWING UP IN THE HOOD AND TRYING TO GIVE YOUR LIFE TO CHRIST DEALING WITH LIFE STRUGGLES IN A TOUGH ENVIRONMENT.
summary: IF YOU NEED A DEEP LAUGH FROM YOUR STOMACH
